<div class="info">
Click <b>"time to eat"</b> for any burgers waiting on the left. Once you've eaten your burger, there's really only once place left for it to go. Click the toilet to make it vanish! Don't see a burger you want to eat, order your very own one-of-a-kind burger below and click <b>"Order IT"</b> to have one of our chefs prepare it for you.
</div>

<div class="row showBorder"> 
  <div class="col-sm-4">
   
   <h2> Ready to eat </h2>
    <ul>
      {{#each burger}}
      {{#if status}}
      <li class="burgerToEat" data-id="{{idburgers}}"">  <img src="./assets/img/burger.png"  alt="burger icon" width="50" height="50">  
        {{name}} 
        <img src="./assets/img/eatit.png"  alt="burger icon" width="50" height="50" style="float:right" title="Eat it yum yum"> 
        </li>
       {{/if}}
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
  
  </div>


  <div class="col-sm-4">

    
   <h2>Order a burger</h2>
    <form class="create-form">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="ca" >Burger Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="ca" name="name">
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="float:right">Order it! </button>
    </form>


  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-4">
    <h2> Eaten </h2>

      {{#each burger}}
      {{#if status}}
      {{else}}
      <li class="burgerToEat" data-id="{{idburgers}}"">  <img src="./assets/img/toilet.jpg"  alt="burger icon" width="50" height="50">  
        {{name}} 
        <img src="./assets/img/flush.png"  alt="burger icon" width="50" height="50" style="float:right" title="Flush IT!"> 
        </li>
       {{/if}}
      {{/each}} 
      </div>